About

I am currently a second year Computer Systems Engineering student at Carleton University in Ottawa aspiring to become a software engineer. The purpose of this site is to have a place for me to showcase my software projects as well as track the progression of my struggles and success throughout my journey. Feel free to browse around!

Since January of 2015, I have been a Software Developer Co-op student at IBM here in Ottawa. I've been working within the Report Studio Development team doing mainly UI development. I am currently on the search for my next co-op term scheduled to start September 2015. If you're interested in getting to know me, feel free to get in touch with me anytime!
